title: dungeon crawl400b26-w32
description:
An old game with very DnD style dungeon crawling.
It uses ASCII graphics and all you need is to download it and double click the .EXE file to start playing (though a read through the instructions is useful)

I haven't had any issues starting and playing on several differnt windows based OS's but if you experience any problems please post it in the comments. (any solutions would also be helpful if they were posted)
